name: Reborn Baby Girl ~ALEXA~Natali Blick
description:
Alexa was made  from her kit sculpted by German artist Natali Blick.  She is 22" with bent legs and weighs appx 5.5 lbs. Layers of Genesis Heat Set paints to achieve her Skintones;   Hand Painted Eyebrows, Rooted Eyelashes, Manicured Fingers and Toes, Magnetic  Pacifier and Hair Bow, Hand Rooted  Premium  Medium Brown Mohair.  Alexa will arrive home with: Onesie
Earrings-Floral Bubble Dress with Panties- Socks and Fresh  Diaper-Magnetic Hair Bow-Magnetic Pacifier (Magnets are strong - Be careful around pacemakers)-PJ's-Certificate and Care Instructions

name: AA Reborn Baby Lila Strydom
description:
This African-American Reborn baby is from a sculpt by Romie Strydom; She is a limited edition 72/600.  Lila is 22 inches and weighs 6 lbs 7 oz.
Lila will  arrive home with: Black/White striped Onesie with matching diaper cover-White onesie with capped sleeves-Black/White dot pinafore-Black/White check shorts-Black/White Tutu with matching Headband-White Headband and Hair Ornaments-Black/White Mary Jane socks-Black/White Sandals
Earrings-Extra Diaper-Magnetic Hair Bow and Pacifier (be careful around Pacemakers)-Romie's Certificate of Authenticity-Care Instructions
